Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 27. GET ALL BOOKINGS - PAGE 2 WITH CUSTOM PAGE SIZE
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/booking?page=2&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 28. GET ALL BOOKINGS - FIRST 5 ITEMS
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/booking?page=1&pageSize=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

