###

### 28. GET ONLY INACTIVE ROOMS
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/room?isActive=false
Accept: application/json

###

### 29. GET ACTIVE ROOMS IN SPECIFIC LOCATION
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/room?location=CapeTown&isActive=true
Accept: application/json

###

### 30. GET INACTIVE ROOMS IN SPECIFIC LOCATION
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/room?location=London&isActive=false
Accept: application/json

###

### 31. GET ALL ROOMS IN LOCATION (Active + Inactive)
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/api/room?location=Johannesburg
Accept: application/json

